high_descs: Turn to the right and find the round table.
Pick up the keys from the back of the table.
Place the keys on the plate in between the computers on the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Carry the plate and turn around, then left and face the coffee table on the right.
Place the plate on the coffee table, on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move keys and a plate to the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the round table.
Pick up the set of keys off of the round table.
Put the set of keys on the plate that is on the round table.
Pick up the plate with the keys on it off of the table.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk over to the coffee table.
Put the plate with the keys on it on the coffee table in front of the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with keys on it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Pick up keys off of table
Put keys on plate on table
Pick up plate with keys off of table
Turn around, walk past table, turn left, walk forward past table, turn left, walk forward, turn right facing coffee table
Put plate with keys on coffee table
anns.task_desc: Pick up keys with plate off of kitchen table and move to coffee table
